Data-VString version 0.0.1
==========================

Perl extension to handle v-strings (often used as version strings)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module recommends

  Test::Pod

TO DO

